net.i2p.router.client

Class LookupDestJob

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.i2p.router.JobImpl
      • net.i2p.router.client.LookupDestJob
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Job

    class LookupDestJob
extends JobImpl
    Look up the lease of a hash, to convert it to a Destination for the client. Or, since 0.9.11, lookup a hostname in the naming service.

                     Hash h,
                     String name,
                     Hash fromLocalDest)
        One of h or name non-null. For hash or b32 name, the dest will be returned if the LS can be found, even if the dest uses unsupported crypto.
        Parameters:
        reqID - must be >= 0 if name != null
        sessID - must non-null if reqID >= 0
        fromLocalDest - use these tunnels for the lookup, or null for exploratory
        Since:
        0.9.11
